{"type":"message","id":"3a455383","parentId":"f3ba2b4c","timestamp":"2026-04-02T14:38:18.608Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Thu 2026-04-02 22:38 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 搜索企业数字化转型、智能安防、网络系统集成、IT运维服务等道简网络相关行业的最新动态，整理3-5条关键信息，返回完整内容。"}],"timestamp":1775140698605}}
{"type":"message","id":"e1bb3d70","parentId":"3a455383","timestamp":"2026-04-02T14:38:23.827Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The subagent task is to search for the latest news related to DaoJian Network's industries: enterprise digital transformation, intelligent security, network system integration, and IT operations services. I need to find 3-5 key pieces of information and return the complete content.\n\nLet me use the web search skill to find this information.","thinkingSignature":"fcfc9b958faa24557438cba84f31338ce9388a1076b85cd97942b6d98c9e219c"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_4stl5l0te38u_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"~/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":117,"output":107,"cacheRead":18914,"cacheWrite":23064,"totalTokens":42202,"cost":{"input":0.0000351,"output":0.0001284,"cacheRead":0.0005674199999999999,"cacheWrite":0.00276768,"total":0.0034985999999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775140698607}}
{"type":"message","id":"173576ca","parentId":"e1bb3d70","timestamp":"2026-04-02T14:38:23.833Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_4stl5l0te38u_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775140703830}}
{"type":"message","id":"a7b9c4b1","parentId":"173576ca","timestamp":"2026-04-02T14:38:29.397Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I'll search for information related to DaoJian Network's industries. Let me do multiple searches to gather comprehensive information.","thinkingSignature":"4682d5422cf510a9c0e0472348702734bc6dab56d6b7030c3bfca24d129fd449"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ggqp9u4e7pox_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型 2026 最新政策动态\" --output json 2>/dev/null | head -200","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ggqp9u4e7pox_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防行业 2026 最新动态趋势\" --output json 2>/dev/null | head -200","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ggqp9u4e7pox_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"网络系统集成 IT运维服务 2026 最新动态\" --output json 2>/dev/null | head -200","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":834,"output":213,"cacheRead":41883,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42930,"cost":{"input":0.0002502,"output":0.0002556,"cacheRead":0.0012564899999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00176229}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775140703832}}
